thread.title_full: Planet of the Vapes reviewed by Megan

author: Megan
title: Megan
text: Ordering was easy, shipping was cheap and arrived faster than I thought it would! All the product was of high quality and the packaging was good as well. The free grinder was much larger and higher quality than I thought it would be and the other container is very nice as well. All in all, i'm very satisfied! I will be ordering from planet of the vapes again.
